name: test_negative_delete_task_by_id
description: Generate random task ID and try to delete it without permission, validate that received error message and code equal to expected

steps.name: Delete task by ID: 763, expected status code: 401

Create url with base url and endpoint: /task/763
Result URL: https://api.clickup.com/api/v2/task/763
Send DELETE request to https://api.clickup.com/api/v2/task/763 with json=None and data=None, expected status code 401
